1. Keep responses under 150 words unless patient asks for detail
1. For exact surgery costs → explain it depends on case complexity, recommend consultation`;

// ── Claude API call ───────────────────────────────────────
async function callClaude(userId, userMessage) {
// Get or create conversation history for this user
if (!conversations[userId]) {
conversations[userId] = [];
}

// Add user message
conversations[userId].push({ role: ‘user’, content: userMessage });

// Keep last 20 messages to manage context window
if (conversations[userId].length > 20) {
conversations[userId] = conversations[userId].slice(-20);
}

const response = await fetch(‘https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages’, {
method: ‘POST’,
headers: {
‘Content-Type’: ‘application/json’,
‘x-api-key’: ANTHROPIC_API_KEY,
‘anthropic-version’: ‘2023-06-01’
},
body: JSON.stringify({
model: ‘claude-sonnet-4-20250514’,
max_tokens: 1000,
system: SYSTEM_PROMPT,
messages: conversations[userId]
})
});

const data = await response.json();
const reply = data.content?.map(b => b.text || ‘’).join(’’) || ‘عذراً، حدث خطأ. يرجى المحاولة مجدداً.’;

// Save assistant reply to history
conversations[userId].push({ role: ‘assistant’, content: reply });

return reply;
}

// ── Parse AI response for tags ────────────────────────────
function parseResponse(rawReply) {
let text = rawReply;
let action = null;

if (text.includes(’[URGENT_HANDOVER]’)) {
text = text.replace(’[URGENT_HANDOVER]’, ‘’).trim();
action = ‘urgent_handover’;
} else if (text.includes(’[BOOKING_REQUEST]’)) {
text = text.replace(’[BOOKING_REQUEST]’, ‘’).trim();
action = ‘booking_request’;
} else if (text.includes(’[HUMAN_HANDOVER]’)) {
text = text.replace(’[HUMAN_HANDOVER]’, ‘’).trim();
action = ‘human_handover’;
}

return { text, action };
}

// ── Main Webhook Endpoint ─────────────────────────────────
// ManyChat External Request step calls this URL
app.post(’/chat’, async (req, res) => {
try {
const { user_id, message } = req.body;

```
if (!user_id || !message) {
  return res.status(400).json({ error: 'Missing user_id or message' });
}

const rawReply = await callClaude(user_id, message);
const { text, action } = parseResponse(rawReply);

// ManyChat expects this response format
// The 'action' field triggers different flows in ManyChat
res.json({
  version: 'v2',
  content: {
    messages: [{ type: 'text', text }],
    actions: action ? [{ action: 'set_field', field_name: 'ai_action', value: action }] : [],
  }
});
```

} catch (err) {
console.error(‘Error:’, err);
res.status(500).json({
version: ‘v2’,
content: {
messages: [{ type: ‘text’, text: ‘عذراً حدث خطأ، يرجى التواصل معنا مباشرة.\nSorry, an error occurred. Please contact us directly.’ }]
}
});
}
});

// ── Reset conversation (optional endpoint) ────────────────
app.post(’/reset’, (req, res) => {
const { user_id } = req.body;
if (user_id && conversations[user_id]) {
delete conversations[user_id];
}
res.json({ success: true });
});

// ── Health check ──────────────────────────────────────────
app.get(’/’, (req, res) => {
res.json({ status: ‘HerniaCore AI Webhook running ✅’ });
});

const PORT = process.env.PORT || 3000;
app.listen(PORT, () => console.log(`Server running on port ${PORT}`));
